<li id="cite_note-CLUE-19">^ <a href="#cite_ref-CLUE_19-0" title=""><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-CLUE_19-1" title=""><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-CLUE_19-2" title=""><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?sec=health&amp;res=9D04E3DE163BF932A05756C0A965948260" class="external text" title="http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?sec=health&amp;res=9D04E3DE163BF932A05756C0A965948260" rel="nofollow">"A CLUE TO THE DECLINE OF ROME"</a>. 31 MAY 1983<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?sec=health&amp;res=9D04E3DE163BF932A05756C0A965948260" class="external free" title="http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?sec=health&amp;res=9D04E3DE163BF932A05756C0A965948260" rel="nofollow">http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?sec=health&amp;res=9D04E3DE163BF932A05756C0A965948260</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 11 JAN 2009</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=A+CLUE+TO+THE+DECLINE+OF+ROME&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.date=31+MAY+1983&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fquery.nytimes.com%2Fgst%2Ffullpage.html%3Fsec%3Dhealth%26res%3D9D04E3DE163BF932A05756C0A965948260&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Decline_of_the_Roman_Empire"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-Krakatoa-20"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Krakatoa_20-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFWinchester2003">Winchester, Simon (2003). <i>Krakatoa: The Day the World Exploded, <span class="mw-formatted-date" title="1883-08-27"><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="08-27"><a href="/wiki/August_27" title="August 27">August 27</a></span>, <a href="/wiki/1883" title="1883">1883</a></span></i>. HarperCollins. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0066212855" class="internal">ISBN 0-06-621285-5</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Krakatoa%3A+The+Day+the+World+Exploded%2C+%5B%5BAugust+27%5D%5D%2C+%5B%5B1883%5D%5D&amp;rft.aulast=Winchester&amp;rft.aufirst=Simon&amp;rft.au=Winchester%2C+Simon&amp;rft.date=2003&amp;rft.pub=HarperCollins&amp;rft.isbn=0-06-621285-5&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Decline_of_the_Roman_Empire"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
